    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"tada\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f389\" role=\"img\" title=\"tada\">:tada:</span> </p>\n<p>It's already nice how \"weakly monotonic, right-continuous map\" collapses to \"limit-preserving functor\".</p>",
